snippet.title: Phoenix Point Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Official Trailer for Phoenix Point, the upcoming tactical combat and strategy game by Julian Gollop.

You can find more information about Phoenix Point on our official website https://www.phoenixpoint.info

Available for pre-order now with instant access to our development builds with the Luxury Digital Edition and above.

Follow us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PhoenixPointGame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Phoenix_Point
Join or forums: https://forums.snapshotgames.com/
Or chat in our Discord http://discord.gg/phoenixpoint

#phoenixpoint #indiedev #juliangollop
